Ngelantur. Kau mau menipuku?

186
00:16:34,099 --> 00:16:35,220
Kemari.

187
00:16:36,609 --> 00:16:38,527
Hong Baksa-nim, ini Kang Seong Mo.

188
00:16:50,048 --> 00:16:51,300
Hong Baksa-nim?

189
00:16:54,388 --> 00:16:55,928
