215
00:18:12,169 --> 00:18:13,168
Apartemen Yeongseong?

216
00:18:13,169 --> 00:18:15,117
Akan kupertimbangkan.

217
00:18:15,568 --> 00:18:16,578
Kau tak paham?

218
00:18:17,338 --> 00:18:18,823
Aku akan mengingatnya.

219
00:18:18,979 --> 00:18:21,037
