346
00:25:26,301 --> 00:25:28,523
Kenapa kau bawa-bawa itu di sini?

347
00:25:29,771 --> 00:25:31,559
Detektif Eun.

348
00:25:34,610 --> 00:25:37,010
Kedua kasus itu terlalu mirip.

349
